# SPDX-License-Identifier: Apache-2.0
# Keep the Docker build context small and reproducible: install + build happen
# INSIDE the image, so host node_modules / dist / VCS must not leak in.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.git
.github
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log

# never ship secrets or local operational material into an image context
.claude-env
**/.claude-env
.aithos/
docs/internal/
deploy/container/run/

# test-only + non-runtime material the gateway image does not need
**/test
**/*.test.*
**/*.xlsx
*.ethos
!birth/aithos-birth.ethos
